      <div class="item-header"><IconChip /><h2>Our Approach</h2></div>
      <p>Commercially available wearable devices feature increasingly sophisticated sensors at affordable prices, without the stigma associated with medical-looking hardware. Our approach focuses on data collected from consumer wearables and mobile phones to capture <b>longitudinal and contextualized data</b> through multimodal affective computing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rationale-item">
      <div class="item-header"><IconEye /><h2>Our Vision</h2></div>
